{"tid":2176394,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"入境處拒發HKFP資深編輯工作簽證","createTime":"2020-08-27T05:20:56.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-29T04:06:26.000Z","uid":78047,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"63f882d2a854fb22da606b56df5bcd7ffc885a5d","tid":2176394,"uid":78047,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-27T05:20:56.000Z","msg":"唔同政府部門繼續助紂為虐<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hkcnews.com/article/33289/hong_kong_free_press-%E5%B7%A5%E4%BD%9C%E7%B0%BD%E8%AD%89-%E8%A8%98%E8%80%85-33302/hong-kong-free-press%E7%94%B3%E8%AB%8B%E8%B3%87%E6%B7%B1%E7%B7%A8%E8%BC%AF%E5%B7%A5%E4%BD%9C%E7%B0%BD%E8%AD%89%E8%A2%AB%E6%8B%92-%E5%85%A5%E5%A2%83%E8%99%95%E5%86%87%E8%A7%A3%E9%87%8B%E7%90%86%E7%94%B1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhkcnews.com%2Farticle%2F33289%2Fhong_kong_free_press-%25E5%25B7%25A5%25E4%25BD%259C%25E7%25B0%25BD%25E8%25AD%2589-%25E8%25A8%2598%25E8%2580%2585-33302%2Fhong-kong-free-press%25E7%2594%25B3%25E8%25AB%258B%25E8%25B3%2587%25E6%25B7%25B1%25E7%25B7%25A8%25E8%25BC%25AF%25E5%25B7%25A5%25E4%25BD%259C%25E7%25B0%25BD%25E8%25AD%2589%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E6%258B%2592-%25E5%2585%25A5%25E5%25A2%2583%25E8%2599%2595%25E5%2586%2587%25E8%25A7%25A3%25E9%2587%258B%25E7%2590%2586%25E7%2594%25B1&d=a8feNXbjtso6d%2BC97Zvpk%2Fo5m3Xr9SEp5dZU2qkndIk%3D&h=232d51b6\" target=\"_blank\">https://hkcnews.com/article/33289/hong_kong_free_press-%E5%B7%A5%E4%BD%9C%E7%B0%BD%E8%AD%89-%E8%A8%98%E8%80%85-33302/hong-kong-free-press%E7%94%B3%E8%AB%8B%E8%B3%87%E6%B7%B1%E7%B7%A8%E8%BC%AF%E5%B7%A5%E4%BD%9C%E7%B0%BD%E8%AD%89%E8%A2%AB%E6%8B%92-%E5%85%A5%E5%A2%83%E8%99%95%E5%86%87%E8%A7%A3%E9%87%8B%E7%90%86%E7%94%B1</a><br />\n<br />\n香港入境處拒絕發給本地英文網媒Hong Kong Free Press（HKFP）一名資深編輯工作簽證。HKFP等候了將近六個月，周二獲入境處電郵通知拒發簽證，但未提供理由。總編輯Tom Grundy要求政府解釋拒發簽證原因，並認為在國安法環境下，他們已成為被攻擊目標。HKFP考慮就拒簽上訴。<br />\n<br />\nTom Grundy指，由於前所未見的簽證延誤，許多新聞機構目前仍陷入困境。HKFP是本地新聞機構，而即將就任的編輯來自愛爾蘭，原本在香港的Bloomberg工作，準備轉工到HKFP。Grundy認為拒發簽證並非中美貿易爭議下的一項針鋒相對的措施，「似乎由於我們的公正及基於事實的報導，我們已在國安法環境下成為攻擊目標。（It appears we have been targeted under the climate of the new security law and because of our impartial and fact-based coverage.）」<br />\n<br />\n他續說，在國安法下，其他行業都有機會會遭受類似的遭遇，很多公司已經因而離港，可能令香港不再是建立總部或基地的合適場所。<br />\n<br />\n保護記者委員會亞洲項目協調員（Committee to Protect Journalists）批評，拒發簽證對香港新聞自由造成重擊，亦嚴重損害了香港作為國際城市和金融中心的地位。無國界記者組織（Reporters Without Borders）東亞辦事處主任 C&eacute;dric Alviani則表示，港府必須撤回這明顯違反新聞自由的決定，認為拒發簽證是反映國安法後新聞自由加速下降的另一標誌。<br />\n<br />\n香港外國記者會（FCC）月初已發聲明，表示留意到駐港外國記者的簽證有被拖延處理的情况。"},{"pid":"cd4da40db47b346a271f21621750d23cbb714b91","tid":2176394,"uid":53026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-27T05:27:24.000Z","msg":"就快被支那邊防取代，慳唔少<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"122665ef37b59810670c39efb44fe7f09654cd59","tid":2176394,"uid":150852,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-27T05:29:08.000Z","msg":"入境好黃<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"27c165acb3434033099f7826e13b5143f1a45392","tid":2176394,"uid":95577,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-27T05:30:48.000Z","msg":"依加immi新加左個政治審查部<br />\n加得就真係預左會揀人續"},{"pid":"b84f96e82b917ade508246202035756164b3b1fc","tid":2176394,"uid":43062,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-27T05:34:27.000Z","msg":"對外國記者咁樣搞我真係唔明點解仲叫有面叫香港國際大都會<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n柒少陣啦港共，個個記者外國勢力寫臭你咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1d6c8d4fab56cd5fcd3296ec8fa7d32335828632","tid":2176394,"uid":48604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"122665ef37b59810670c39efb44fe7f09654cd59","tid":21763